ßIN LOVING MEMORY OF BART MOORE-GILBERT, 1952-2015
Beloved father, lovely husband, dear friend, fabulous writer
We miss you so much, but you live on in our hearts
Love always, your 'sniggle' family, Anna, Maddy and Luke xxx"Ņ
ļGood night sweet Prince and may
flights of angels sing you to your rest.
Thank you for being my friend.
JD

Neil Young
11th April 1961 - 15th July 2019
You were our sunshine
Ali, Izzie, Charlotte, Family & Friends
Forever in our hearts"¾
